パッケージ tokyo.nakanaka

クラス MapHolder

java.lang.Object
tokyo.nakanaka.MapHolder
public class MapHolder extends Object
A class for the String expression "<name>[<key>=<value>...]", or just "<name>". (It has no key and values in the case) The keys and values must be String.
